				<td colspan="2"><span>Bard Taunt ----&gt; DA song.
<br />

<br />
If you need to use DA song a lot, then what you need is a better pulling skill.
<br />

<br />
If tank can't get agro, you need a new tank.
<br />

<br />
Having a Taunt song would mean rewriting the songs code so that we get the same agro as of... a chanter for example. That way we would have no problem getting agro, but without the chanter runes it could be quite painful.
<br />

