<br />

<br />
I sure do.  It's part of my standard hard LDON lineup.
<br />

<br />
I'm starting to sound like a broken record here, but I'm very enamored of DA. 
<br />

<br />
-- Lets me proximity pull singles I couldn't otherwise pull by reducing chain agro.
<br />

<br />
-- Makes it easy for me to target those annoying around-the-corner out of LOS mobs without getting pummelled.
<br />

<br />
-- Lets me get back to the group with 0 damage on obnoxious pulls, like those d*mn rooms in Guk with the planks over a water pool. . . . you know, the ones where the d*mn plank doesn't line up with the door.
<br />

<br />
-- Lets me save people who are about to die.  My regular group knows what to do if DA pops on outta nowhere.  Everybody but the about-to-die person clicks it off.
<br />

<br />
DA owns.  </span></td>
